{
  "texts": [
    "However, if carefully prompted and with instructor oversight Generative AI can play the role of tutor, interacting with the student via open-ended questions, checking on prior knowledge, providing multiple examples, and challenging students to generate their own knowledge.",
    "This type of prompting uses the AI's capacity to role play and adapt to specific instructions.",
    "Because the AI it can be prompted to \"act\" like a tutor, it can be instructed to draw the student out in conversation and focus their attention to specific known sticking points or misconceptions of a topic.",
    "Instructors, with expertise in teaching a specific topic can customize tutors for specific use cases or topics and prompt those tutors to guide students.",
    "As in all cases of students working with AI, there are inherent risks in the process, and we explore some of these below."
  ]
}